npm install webpack@1.15.0

bundle the app from local installed webpack:
.\"node_modules/.bin/webpack" ./js/webpack/app.js build/bundles/bundle.js


bundle the app from globally installed webpack:
webpack ./js/webpack/app.js build/bundles/bundle.js


With custom config:
.\"node_modules/.bin/webpack"



watch mode:
.\"node_modules/.bin/webpack" --watch

webpack dev server to serve local files:
http://localhost:3000/webpack-dev-server/index.html - show the app within iframe beneath the status bar
http://localhost:3000 - show the app without status bar. To get live reload changes in browser, pass --inline argument like below only for this case

.\"node_modules/.bin/webpack" --inline --watch -> 



